The '''Narodowy Instytut Zdrowia Publicznego – Państwowy Zakład Higieny''' ([[English language|English]]: '''National Institute of Public Health - National Institute of Hygiene''') is a [[research institute]] in [[Polish people|Poland]] focused on [[public health]]. It was founded on 21 November 1918.

